<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV45">
<l>maṇṇuḷāykol viṇṇuḷāykol maṇṇuḷēma yaṅkiniṉ</l>
<l>ṟeṇṇumeṇṇa kappaṭāykol leṉṉamāyai niṉṟamar</l>
<l>kaṇṇuḷāykol cēyaikola ṉantaṉmēlki ṭantavem</l>
<l>puṇṇiyāpu ṉantuḻāya laṅkalampu ṉitaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You are on the earth! You are in the sky! You will not be grasped</l>
<l>By the thoughts of those who think, being confused in [this] world!</l>
<l>What wonder is it that [that] You are [visible] to the eyes of Your people!</l>
<l>You are distant [to the others]! O our holy [Lord] who recline on Ananta!</l>
<l rend="indent">O pure, beautiful [Lord] with garlands of tulasi from the uplands!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
